
OPUS/tools
A collection of various tools and scripts
-----------------------------------------


recode      a perlish character encoding conversion (handles malformed data?)
tab2tmx     simplistic conversion of TAB-separated parallel corpora to TMX
xces2moses  simplistic converter from XCES format to Moses format
xces2text   convert parallel corpora in XCES format to text format
xces2tmx    convert parallel corpora in XCES format to TMX
xces2plain  yet another XCES to text converter (based on XML::DT and XML::XCES)



OLD SUBDIR STRUCTURE

opus ........ OPUS-specific tools & scripts
public ...... freely available tools
academic .... tools freely available for research purposes
nonfree ..... non-free or licensed tools



possibly interesting tools:

* fast text extraction from XML with xmlcutty: https://github.com/miku/xmlcutty
